name: I - The Magician
description: My version of the tarot, card I “The Magician” in reference to the northeast region of Brazil, where there is a real struggle of man in adapting to the hot, dry and arid environment. This will be a collection of the 22 major arcana. I present to you the first card, containing all the deep symbology of the tarot and now deservedly represented by these warrior people.
